{"tid":1466210,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔撚再話我地唔需要形象/光環/民意","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:24.000Z","uid":249718,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33ab015105df6d0b40c756cf8fec5fa0de15c7b5","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"過咗今晚 希望咁多位手足唔好再亂咁屌人左膠<br />\n冷靜分析再勸阻一啲唔合理嘅事嘅發生 絕對唔係左膠<br />\n<br />\n第一 話唔care光環個啲 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為警察就曬殺曬啲記者都唔會有後果 佢地照有人撐 但我地唔同啊！我地咁嘅時勢係好撚需要支持啊！</span></span>今日機場一役已經開始有反感 唔係話一定要全世界支持 但我地係咪應該要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡可能</span></span>爭取支持同埋去避免唔好比人有位入？香港去到一個臨界點 大家都同意 但其實我地都係<br />\n大家開始疑心疑鬼 開始割（把口就話無）個種信任已經消失咗 點解當時我地會咁自信？好大程度係因為民意歸向我地啊 200萬人做我地backup啊！大家真係要再冷靜啲 真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一子錯滿盤皆落索 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔做嘢絕對係好過做錯野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第二 我覺得依家唯一可以做到嘅 係文宣要拋棄道德底線 黑都要講到白 過咗今晚我地已經要豪賭 老屈都係咁話 依家呢個社會 文宣嘅威力隨時大過你出手打人 唔好唔記得我地文宣嘅努力啊！！！"},{"pid":"af92a52be3075c2e020db28cdcfca12b251342e3","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d53ec2c1d8b25f4c1414a9704ce5013b32d0159e","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"534439d26eefab5c7578d490e0951e1dcc634bc3","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"762eac05d4561471fc35a74b2783672a4fe36aa4","tid":1466210,"uid":181363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"推..."},{"pid":"c1931d6a1315a83ffbd3bda1970ddf76e9e8c96f","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab841f15bbdd88d20ac4ce4a9ac529a38755f4a7","tid":1466210,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"只可以講<br />\n我地屬於明 佢地係暗<br />\n佢地暗做乜7都得 就算殺人 咩嘢那渣嘢都做齊哂<br />\n但我地攻擊 佢都who fucking care<br />\n但我地做稍為少少過火嘅嘢<br />\n就會一鋪清袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算係動漫同現實世界 明果方面都係咁慘<br />\n唯一唔同正義最後是贏家<br />\n現實我地睇唔到呢加贏定輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b14ede9adb04bc7ce4e9a330d1c5bed37f5d2de","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"各位手足 我地嘅支持係我地大家一齊慢慢累積返嚟㗎 真係要三思 <br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n做錯大家一齊補鑊"},{"pid":"1355590dad5af2454c329d906d92f1ca86a46ad9","tid":1466210,"uid":24318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:01.000Z","msg":"形象係好緊要， 唔好比仇恨主導思想"},{"pid":"527cad46a2373448d2676c85c51449ce29f3a05f","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10d4023aab9c07d9aa72d7d80446cf12c3013281","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e66a8c731866948b294f506bd1b4ff256f77cde","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"ce9117d77f8bea38f697e9481c3b847b6f813ef9","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"724b7610475281e4db3045a21ba1eb8be67d9a05","tid":1466210,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:12.000Z","msg":"推"}